descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains information related to insurance sales incentives. The dataset consist of only 125 records.

The dataset contains the following columns:
Amount, Plan, Term, PPT, Incentive

Amount - Numerical variable. It denotes the insurance premium.
Plan - Categorical variable. It denotes the the type of insurance product.
Term- Numerical variable. It denotes the term of the insurance policy.
PPT - Numerical variable. It denotes the duration of the insurance premium payment.
Incentive - Categorical variable. It denotes whether incentive is achieved or not.

The Incentive variable consists of "Yes" and "No' which denotes whether the incentive is achieved or not.
